(14) Parent means one or both
parents or a stepparent when such stepparent is married to the custodial parent
as of the filing of the petition;

(17) Seal
a record means that a record shall not be available to the public except upon
the order of a court upon good cause shown;

(18) Secure detention means detention in a highly
structured, residential, hardware-secured facility designed to restrict a
juvenile's movement;
